ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This class is a student research workshop intended to improve the quality of students' working papers and enable them to gain experience presenting and discussing early stage work. I would recommend this class to students for honing presentation skills and enabling them to receive feedback from faculty.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: The course enables students to hear each others' ideas and develop them. The seminar enabled me to develop my second year paper into a publication.
